title: Honey, Zeit Shrunk The Trends 2/7: Winter Olympics, Rumble, Pantyhose, National Archives, Kylie Jenner, 'Moonfall'
itunes:title: Honey, Zeit Shrunk The Trends 2/7: Winter Olympics, Rumble, Pantyhose, National Archives, Kylie Jenner, 'Moonfall'
description:
In this edition of Honey, Zeit Shrunk The Trends, Jack and super producer Becca discuss the Winter Olympics, Joe Rogan getting offered a spot on right wing platform Rumble, the COVID pantyhose lifehack courtesy of Cambridge University, the National Archives seizing Trump documents from Mar-a-Lago, Kylie Jenner announcing a new baby, and 'Moonfall' flopping at the box office.
